<p>[PLACEHOLDER — Explain why many teachers and HR professionals prefer a browser-based countdown timer over purpose-built proctoring software for standard timed exercises: no installation required, no accounts, no IT dependencies, works on any device in the room, and can be displayed on a projector or smartboard instantly.]</p>

